@startuml
left to right direction

actor "User" as User

rectangle "Traffic Camera Browser" {

  boundary "Camera Detail + Playback UI\n<<boundary>>" as B1
  control "Playback Controller\n<<control>>" as C1
  entity "Camera Catalog\n<<entity>>" as E1
  entity "Recording Cache (72h)\n<<entity>>" as E2
}

note right of B1
  When a user clicks on a camera, a list
  will appear in the user interface. Users
  can view playback of any camera from the
  past 72 hours through our platform.
end note

User --> B1 : choose time range
B1 --> C1 : playback request
C1 --> E1 : verify camera exists
C1 --> E2 : retrieve video segments
C1 --> B1 : stream playback video

@enduml